snippet.title: YDKJ Facebook - All Special Episodes
snippet.description:
All the Special Episodes in You Don't Know Jack Facebook.

Jack the Halls - Egg your noggin with our special holiday episode. Ho ho no!
2012: Year in Technology - Is this the line for Apps?
Red Carpet & Drapes Gala - And the award for best movie-themed trivia or short subject goes to...
March Derangement - Bust our trivia bracket with your hoops knowledge! Sweatband and short shorts recommended.
Spring Break Wet Trivia - Cancun! Woooooooo!
Sharknado, Sharknado, - Sponsored by Clone Booth
